<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Rayan Fiver | Web & Design Blog</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="A professional blog about web development, design principles, and modern development tools."
  />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container nav-wrap">
      <a href="index.html" class="logo">Rayan Fiver</a>
      <button class="menu-toggle" aria-label="Toggle menu">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>
      <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="#articles">Articles</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="home">
    <section class="hero hero-umme">
      <div class="container hero-banner">
        <div class="hero-main">
          <p class="eyebrow">Welcome to My Blog</p>
          <h1>Rayan Fiver - Web & Design Explorer</h1>
          <p class="subtitle">
            I share insights about responsive web design, UI/UX principles, and modern development tools. Join me on this journey of continuous learning and exploration.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#articles" class="btn btn-primary">Read Articles</a>
            <a href="#about" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="search-section" style="padding: 28px 0 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <label for="searchInput" class="search-label">Search Articles</label>
        <input 
          type="search" 
          id="searchInput" 
          class="search-input" 
          placeholder="Search by topic, keyword..." 
          aria-label="Search blog articles"
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="posts-section" id="articles">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <h2>Latest Articles</h2>
          <p>Exploring web development, design, and digital innovation.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="post-grid" id="postGrid">
          <article class="post-card" data-search="responsive design web layout mobile css html">
            <a href="post1.html" class="post-thumb-link" aria-label="Read responsive design article">
              <img class="post-thumb" src="https://picsum.photos/id/10/900/520" alt="Responsive web design mockup" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <div class="post-content">
              <div class="post-meta-top">
                <span class="badge">Web Design</span>
                <span>15 Apr 2026</span>
              </div>
              <h3>The Future of Responsive Web Design</h3>
              <p>Exploring modern approaches to responsive design, from mobile-first strategies to advanced CSS techniques that adapt to any screen size.</p>
              <div class="post-meta-bottom">
                <span>8 min read</span>
                <a href="post1.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Read More</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card" data-search="ui design principles contrast hierarchy typography color accessibility">
            <a href="post2.html" class="post-thumb-link" aria-label="Read UI design principles article">
              <img class="post-thumb" src="https://picsum.photos/id/25/900/520" alt="Design principles and typography" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <div class="post-content">
              <div class="post-meta-top">
                <span class="badge">Design Principles</span>
                <span>18 Apr 2026</span>
              </div>
              <h3>Essential UI Design Principles</h3>
              <p>Master the fundamentals of UI design including hierarchy, contrast, alignment, and color psychology that every designer should know.</p>
              <div class="post-meta-bottom">
                <span>10 min read</span>
                <a href="post2.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Read More</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-card" data-search="development tools vscode webpack react npm javascript framework">
            <a href="post3.html" class="post-thumb-link" aria-label="Read modern tools article">
              <img class="post-thumb" src="https://picsum.photos/id/180/900/520" alt="Modern development tools and setup" loading="lazy" />
            </a>
            <div class="post-content">
              <div class="post-meta-top">
                <span class="badge">Development</span>
                <span>22 Apr 2026</span>
              </div>
              <h3>Modern Web Development Tools 2026</h3>
              <p>A comprehensive guide to the latest development tools, build systems, and frameworks that are revolutionizing how we build web applications.</p>
              <div class="post-meta-bottom">
                <span>12 min read</span>
                <a href="post3.html" class="btn btn-secondary">Read More</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section" id="about">
      <div class="container about-card about-simple">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
          I'm Rayan Fiver, a passionate web developer and designer exploring the intersection of beautiful design and functional code. Through this blog, I share what I've learned about creating responsive, accessible, and user-friendly web experiences.
        </p>
        <p>
          I believe in the power of clean code, thoughtful design, and continuous learning. Whether you're interested in frontend development, UI/UX design, or the latest web technologies, you'll find valuable insights here.
        </p>
        <p>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/rayanfiver95-design" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/rayanfiver95-design</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="newsletter" id="contact">
      <div class="container newsletter-wrap">
        <div>
          <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
          <p>Email: rayan.fiver.dev@gmail.com</p>
          <p>Location: Digital Innovator</p>
        </div>
        <form class="subscribe-form" id="subscribeForm">
          <input 
            type="email" 
            id="emailInput" 
            placeholder="Your message..." 
            required 
            aria-label="Contact message"
          />
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <p>© 2026 Rayan Fiver's Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/rayanfiver95-design" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="#" aria-label="Twitter">Twitter</a>
      </div>
      <div class="quick-links"></div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
